enchantment.minecraft.channeling.desc.re: Makes Posideon's Fork bring forth a flash when ye squewer a creature. Sets enemy creatures ablaze.
enchantment.minecraft.fire_aspect.desc.r: Sets enemy creatures ablaze. Acts as a Ship's Bane when creepin'.
enchantment.minecraft.luck_of_the_sea.de: Ups the quality of fishing booty and lowers the time needed for fish to bite.
advancements.adventure.two_birds_one_arr: Slaughter two Flyin' Devils with a single bolt
enchantment.minecraft.bane_of_arthropods: Vastly ups hurtin' done to and slows critters.
enchantment.minecraft.binding_curse.desc: Stops yerself from takin' off yer clothing.
enchantment.minecraft.blast_protection.d: Vastly lowers hurtin' taken from booms.
enchantment.minecraft.breach.desc: Brings down the goodness of clothes.
enchantment.minecraft.channeling.desc: Makes Posideon's Fork to bring forth flashes when striking a creature while a storm's a brewin'.
enchantment.minecraft.density.desc: Ups hurtin' done per block plunged.
enchantment.minecraft.feather_falling.de: Vastly lowers hurtin' taken from plunging.
enchantment.minecraft.fire_protection.de: Vastly lowers hurtin' taken from and time spent burnin'.
enchantment.minecraft.frost_walker.desc: Freezes th' ocean below yerself for a bit.
enchantment.minecraft.impaling.desc: Vastly ups hurtin' done to enemy creatures of the deep.
enchantment.minecraft.infinity.desc: Makes normal bolts to not be used up.
enchantment.minecraft.loyalty.desc: Makes Posideon's Fork to fling back towards yerself upon landing.
enchantment.minecraft.luck_of_the_sea.de: Ups the quality of fishing booty.
enchantment.minecraft.lure.desc: Lowers the time needed for fish to bite.
enchantment.minecraft.mending.desc: Makes balls o' wisdom repair the object.
enchantment.minecraft.multishot.desc: Makes three bolts shoot instead of one.
enchantment.minecraft.piercing.desc: Makes ammo pierce through enemy creatures and targes.
enchantment.minecraft.projectile_protect: Vastly lowers hurtin' taken from ammo.
enchantment.minecraft.protection.desc: Lowers hurtin' taken from all sorts of things.
enchantment.minecraft.riptide.desc: Allows yerself to launch yerself with Posideon's Fork when wet.
enchantment.minecraft.smite.desc: Vastly ups hurtin' done to undead.
enchantment.minecraft.soul_speed.desc: Ups movin' speed on soul blocks.
enchantment.minecraft.sweeping_edge.desc: Ups hurtin' done with sweepin' attacks.
enchantment.minecraft.thorns.desc: Hurts foes when ye get hurt yerself.
enchantment.minecraft.vanishing_curse.de: Makes the object vanish on dyin'.
enchantment.minecraft.wind_burst.desc: Makes crushin' attacks launch yerself upward.
enchantment.enchancement.assimilation.de: Make yer hat munch on grub when yerself be hungry all by itself, with yer off hand being focused on. Grub is eaten faster.
enchantment.enchancement.perception.desc: Ups looking in the inky black and makes enemy creatures seeable through walls.
enchantment.enchancement.veil.desc: Lowers monster seeing range and hides yer name behind walls.
enchantment.enchancement.amphibious.desc: Ups under sea breakin' and movin' speed. Lowers air consumption under sea and time spent burnin'. Immediately puts yerself out and allows yerself to use Riptide for a while after leavin' the ocean.
enchantment.enchancement.strafe.desc: Double tapping [%s] launches yerself in yer movin' direction.
enchantment.enchancement.strafe.desc.sin: Pressing [%s] launches yerself in yer movin' direction.
enchantment.enchancement.wardenspine.des: Hurts and blinds foes and greatly lowers hurtin' taken from yer behind.
enchantment.enchancement.adrenaline.desc: Ups movin' speed more and reduces more hurtin' taken the greater ye is to dyin'.
enchantment.enchancement.dash.desc: Pressing [%s] in the air launches yerself the way yer lookin'.
enchantment.enchancement.slide.desc: Holding [%s] while land bound causes yerself to slide constantly. Pressing [%s] in the air causes yerself to fall to the ground like an anchor, flinging back enemy creatures without breakin' yer legs.
enchantment.enchancement.buoy.desc: Makes yerself to walk on the ocean, descending via creepin'. Holding jump while submerged shoots yerself upwards. Stops yerself floating. Gives ye a speed boost after leaving water for a bit.
enchantment.enchancement.bouncy.desc: Stops yer falls hurtin'. Knocks yerself upwards upon landing while not creepin'. Creeping while on land will make yer jump extra big.
enchantment.enchancement.gale.desc: Allows yerself to jump more times while in the air.
enchantment.enchancement.berserk.desc: Ups hurtin' done more the more yerself is missing health.
enchantment.enchancement.frostbite.desc: Freezes enemy creatures ye fight. When they fall, turns them into icey figures that can slide around or shattered, flinging shards o' frost that freeze other enemy creatures.
enchantment.enchancement.chaos.desc: Gives ammo a random negative potion effect, or positive if creepin'.
enchantment.enchancement.delay.desc: Bolts will pause after shooting, building up their ability to hurtin' over time. Can have their fuse cut short by punching, and additionally redirected by creepin'.
enchantment.enchancement.phasing.desc: Makes it so bolts fire straight and true as well as float through blocks, after which they will behave normal-like. Bolts home in on nearby creatures.
enchantment.enchancement.brimstone.desc: Fires a piercing ray that ignores clothes and ups hurtin' with charge and distance. Costs your very life to fire.
enchantment.enchancement.scatter.desc: Allows Shards o' Purple Gems to be used as ammo which explode into a burst of flyin' objects.
enchantment.enchancement.torch.desc: Allows rapid loadin' of Torches that set shot enemy creatures ablaze. Torches that hit a block will be placed if shot while creepin'. Yer Crossbow can only load Torches.
enchantment.enchancement.leech.desc: Regenerates yer life force when ye hurt a creature. Thrown Posideon's Forks will temporarily stick to enemy creatures and hurt 'em.
enchantment.enchancement.warp.desc: Sails yerself to the location of yer Posideon's Fork if it didn't hit a creature.
enchantment.enchancement.extracting.desc: Grabs materials from connected ores, leaving the rock behind. Disabled while creepin'.
enchantment.enchancement.molten.desc: Smelts mined blocks. Disabled while creepin'.
enchantment.enchancement.beheading.desc: Slain enemy creatures and folk have a chance to loose their head.
enchantment.enchancement.lumberjack.desc: Connected logs will also be broken. Disabled while creepin'.
enchantment.enchancement.bury.desc: Using on a mob will bury it like treasure but only if the land be soft enough.
enchantment.enchancement.scooping.desc: Deals extra hurtin' and ups mob booty dropin'.
enchantment.enchancement.disarm.desc: Steals or disables the creature or folk ye got's held object.
enchantment.enchancement.grapple.desc: Allows the Fishin' Bobber to hook onto blocks. Pulls yerself in towards that block when ye release. Reels in creatures with more strength.
subtitles.enchancement.entity.generic.wa: Spine o' the Monstrous Beast activates

enchancement.midnightconfig.allowTreasur: Allow Treasure Magic In Witchcraft Bench
enchancement.midnightconfig.crossbowsPul: Crossbows Pull From yer Loot bag
enchancement.midnightconfig.drownedUseHe: Sunken Sailors Use Held Posideon's Forks
enchancement.midnightconfig.luckOfTheSea: Luck O' Yer Sea Has Stronger Bait
